VInstruct your babies.
p49
aVRemind them that the year has passed to be docile or small.
p50
aVSome of us said for the first time that we were women,
p51
aVtook this oath of solidarity seriously.
p52
aVSome of us bore children and some of us did not,
p53
aVand none of us questioned whether that made us real
p54
aVor appropriate or true.
